0x100CD221F572F6E1// SetPedSurvivesBeingOutOfWater
BOOL _SET_PED_SURVIVES_BEING_OUT_OF_WATER(Ped ped, BOOL toggle);
Parameters:ped: The marine animal pedtoggle: true to allow survival out of water, false to apply normal water restrictions.Returns: Returns true if successful.Allows marine animals to survive outside of water (R* is using it for sharks).NativeDB Introduced: v3407
